Package fr.ens.biologie.generic

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DataContainer
    This to better separate concerns of property list management currently mixed in PropertyListInterface.
    Initialisable
    An object that can be initialised after construction
    Resettable
    3Worlds: component threeWorlds-core
    SaveableAsText
    An interface for objects that can be saved as text (in text files or Strings) and later re-loaded with a (static) valueOf() method.
    Sealable
    This interface for objects that can be modified for a certain time, and then be sealed so that no future change is permitted.
    Showable
    an interface for things that can display themselves graphically in a separate window (for dbugging, mainly)
    Sizeable
    An interface for objects which have a size
    Textable
    For relatively complex objects that can return information with various levels of detail.
    Versionable
    An interface to put version numbers on objects.
    WriteProtectable
    This interface for objects that can be write protected/enabled.
